-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  What is it?
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
A jQuery plugin to get current browser viewport size (page's exact width and height). 

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  Requirements
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- This plugin requires jQuery v1.3.2+

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  Usage guide:
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------	  

	 - To resize element only once.
	  
	   $("#element").fitToPage();
	 
	 - To keep element size in sync with browser size.
	 
	   $("#element").fitToPage(true);
	   
	 - Returns current web page size.
	    
	   var size = $.getPageSize();

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  Support for
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- IE6+
- Firefox 3.0+
- Opera 9+
- Not tested on Chrome and Safari, but plugin expected to work on both the browsers.

